《'''歐洲聯盟去或留？'''》（{{lang-en|The European Union: In or Out?}}）是於2014年4月2日在[[英國廣播公司第二台|英國廣播公司第二台]]直播播出的電視辯論<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2014/mar/10/nick-clegg-v-nigel-farage-ukip-leader-lib-dem | title=Nick Clegg v Nigel Farage? The Ukip leader must be licking his lips | work=The Guardian | date=2014-03-10 | accessdate=2014-03-23 | author=Harris, John | archive-date=2021-03-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309032547/https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2014/mar/10/nick-clegg-v-nigel-farage-ukip-leader-lib-dem | dead-url=no }}</ref>。辯論全長一小時，由{{tsl|en|David Dimbleby|大衛·添布比}}主持，留歐派和脫歐派代表分別為[[尼克·克萊格|尼克·克萊格]]和[[奈杰尔·法拉奇|奈杰尔·法拉奇]]<ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/ukip/10679420/Nick-Clegg-v-Nigel-Farage-clash-of-the-middleweights.html | title=Nick Clegg v Nigel Farage: clash of the middleweights | work=The Daily Telegraph | date=2014-03-05 | accessdate=2014-03-23 | author=Kirkup, James | archive-date=2021-03-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308210732/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/ukip/10679420/Nick-Clegg-v-Nigel-Farage-clash-of-the-middleweights.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。辯論的問題由觀眾提出，留歐派和脫歐派各半。

在此電視辯論前的一周，法拉奇和克萊格已在{{tsl|en|LBC|LBC}}的電台辯論上碰面，由{{tsl|en|Nick Ferrari|力克·法拉利}}主持<ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/news/broadcasters/bbc2-to-host-nick-clegg-and-nigel-farage-debate/5068286.article | title=BBC2 to host Nick Clegg and Nigel Farage debate | work=Broadcast Now | date=2014-03-05 | accessdate=2014-03-23 | author=Kanter, Jake | archive-date=2016-03-03 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225827/http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/news/broadcasters/bbc2-to-host-nick-clegg-and-nigel-farage-debate/5068286.article | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/ukip/10677475/Nick-Clegg-and-Nigel-Farage-to-go-head-to-head-in-live-TV-debate.html | title=Nick Clegg and Nigel Farage to go head to head in live TV debate | work=The Daily Telegraph | date=2014-03-05 | accessdate=2014-03-23 | author=Graham, Georgia | archive-date=2021-03-08 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308165300/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/politics/ukip/10677475/Nick-Clegg-and-Nigel-Farage-to-go-head-to-head-in-live-TV-debate.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/nick-clegg-and-nigel-farage-to-clash-in-headtohead-tv-and-radio-debates-9170111.html | title=Nick Clegg and Nigel Farage to clash in head-to-head TV and radio debates | work=The Independent | date=2014-03-05 | accessdate=2014-03-23 | author=Withnall, Adam | archive-date=2015-09-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925171546/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/politics/nick-clegg-and-nigel-farage-to-clash-in-headtohead-tv-and-radio-debates-9170111.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/news/a555649/nick-clegg-to-take-on-nigel-farage-in-live-bbc-two-debate.html | title=Nick Clegg to take on Nigel Farage in live BBC Two debate | work=Digital Spy | date=2014-03-05 | accessdate=2014-03-23 | author=Eames, Tom | archive-date=2015-10-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151025043749/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/tv/news/a555649/nick-clegg-to-take-on-nigel-farage-in-live-bbc-two-debate.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>。辯論時值[[2014年歐洲議會選舉_(英國)|2014年歐洲議會選舉]]和潛在的[[英國去留歐盟公投|英國去留歐盟公投]]前夕<ref name="Farage v Clegg – the verdict">{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-26864280|title=Farage v Clegg – the verdict|date=2014-04-03|accessdate=2014-04-04|archive-date=2021-03-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210307205804/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-politics-26864280|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[YouGov|YouGov]]和{{tsl|en|ICM Research|ICM研究中心|ICM}}的民調顯示法拉奇表現較為優勝<ref name=":0">{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2014/04/02/farage-wins-polls-second-eu-debate_n_5078850.html|title=Nigel Farage Wins Second European Union Debate Against Nick Clegg|date=2014-04-02|accessdate=2014-04-04|archive-date=2017-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171018191728/http://www.huffingtonpost.co.uk/2014/04/02/farage-wins-polls-second-eu-debate_n_5078850.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，前者指出68%受訪者認為法拉奇表現最好，只有27%認為是克萊格；衛報與ICM的聯合民調結果也是類近<ref name=":0" />。BBC的{{tsl|en|Nick Robinson (journalist)|力克·羅便臣}}分析指出「歷史會記下法拉奇贏了這些辯論；曾挑戰英國非建制派的克萊格會希望他或許因此也有一些勝利」<ref name="Farage v Clegg – the verdict"/>。

